com.ca.mas.identity.common

Class MASFilteredRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ca.mas.identity.common.MASFilteredRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MASFilteredRequestBuilder, MASPagination

    public class MASFilteredRequest
extends java.lang.Object
implements MASFilteredRequestBuilder, MASPagination

    MASFilteredRequest describes the APIs for user's to specify scim filters. This interface would be the backing set of APIs so that an application developer could provide a simple query system for identity management.
